text: Two Cars, One Night is a 2004 New Zealand short drama movie directed by Taika Waititi and starring Rangi Ngamoki and Hutini Waikato. It was nominated for an Academy Award in 2005. ==Other websites== * * *Two Cars, One Night at NZ On Screen Category:2004 drama movies Category:Short movies Category:New Zealand drama movies Category:Movies directed by Taika Waititi
